<head>
   <style>
       /*
 * === BASE STYLES ===
 */
*,
*::before,
*::after {
  box-sizing: border-box;
  transition: all 2s easy;
  //border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0, .2);
}

.formbdy {
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0;
  width: 400px;
  background-color: #f1f1f1;
  font: 14px sans-serif;
}

.formdiv {
    border-radius: 5px;
    background-color: transparent;
    padding: 40px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 13px #929292; 
}

.h1sf {
    margin-top: 50px;
    text-align: center;
    display: block;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: rgba(0,0,0, .13);
}


/*
 * === INPUTS, SELECT ===
 */
.intx {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 13px;
    margin: 8px 0;
    display: inline-block;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 4px;
    -webkit-transition: 0.5s;
    transition: 0.5s;
    outline: none;
}

.intx:focus, select:focus {
    border: 1px solid #99b3ff;
}

.intx:focus::-webkit-input-placeholder {
  color: transparent;
}

.bcbtn {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #668cff;
    color: white;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    margin: 8px 0 0;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    transition: 0.5s;
    height: 55px;
    &:hover { background-color: #4d79ff; }
}

.bc {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100px;
    margin: 8px 0;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    font-family: sans-serif;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    border-radius: 4px;
    resize: none;
    outline: none;
  
    &:focus { border: 1px solid #99b3ff; }
}

.page-item {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0px 9px;
    margin-right: 4px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: solid 1px #c0c0c0;
    background: #e9e9e9;
    box-shadow: inset 0px 1px 0px rgba(255,255,255, .8), 0px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0, .1);
    font-size: .875em;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #717171;
    text-shadow: 0px 1px 0px rgba(255,255,255, 1);
}

.page-item:hover, .page.gradient:hover {
    background: #fefefe;
    background: -webkit-gradient(linear, 0% 0%, 0% 100%, from(#FEFEFE), to(#f0f0f0));
    background: -moz-linear-gradient(0% 0% 270deg,#FEFEFE, #f0f0f0);
}

.page-item.active {
    border: none;
    background: #616161;
    box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 8px rgba(0,0,0, .5), 0px 1px 0px rgba(255,255,255, .8);
    color: #f0f0f0;
    text-shadow: 0px 0px 3px rgba(0,0,0, .5);
}


   </style>
    
</head>
<h1 style="font-size:50px; text-align: center;" >방명록</h1>
<p style="font-size:20px; text-align: center;">안녕하세요. 모의수강신청서비스를 하고 있는 단국대 멋쟁이 사자처럼입니다.</p>
<p style="font-size:20px; text-align: center;">다소 부족함이 많은 서비스 이용해 주셔서 감사합니다.</p>
<p style="font-size:20px; text-align: center;">방명록에 응원의 한마디 적어주시면 큰 힘이 됩니당!</p>
<p style="font-size:20px; text-align: center; margin-bottom:20px;">이용해주시는 여러분이 있어 저희가 있습니다. 항상 감사합니다.</p>
<div class="formbdy">
    

    
    
    <div class="formdiv">  
        <form action="/board/create">
            <!-- first name -->
            <label>작성자이름</label>
            <input class="intx" type="text" id="fname" placeholder="이름" name="name"></input>
    
            <!-- message -->
            <label>내용</label>
            <textarea class="bc" type="text" placeholder="내용" name="content"></textarea>
    
            <!-- <CTA></CTA> -->
            <input class="bcbtn" type="submit" value="작성!"></form>
    </div>

</div>
            <table class="table">
                  <thead>
                    <tr class="th_tr_1">
                      <th class="th_1">#</th>
                      <th>내용</th>
                      <th>작성자</th>
                    </tr>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody>
                      <% @posts.each do |h| %>
                            <tr class="tb_tr">
                                <td class="td_1 tb_td">
                                    <%= h.id %>
                                </td>
                                <td class = "tb_td">
                                    <%= h.content %>
                                </td>
                                <td class="sc tb_td">
                                    <%= h.user %>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                      <% end %>
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <%= paginate @posts %>
            
           